WEBVTT

00:00:00.917 --> 00:00:03.643
Mislite li da će današnje građevine

00:00:03.787 --> 00:00:06.033
u budućnosti itko smatrati čudom?

00:00:07.042 --> 00:00:08.684
Pomislite na Stonehenge,

00:00:08.708 --> 00:00:10.226
piramide,

00:00:10.250 --> 00:00:12.917
Machu Picchu i Uskršnji otok.

00:00:14.167 --> 00:00:18.143
Takva je arhitektura 
drukčija od današnje,

00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:20.712
s onim masivnim kamenjem,

00:00:20.712 --> 00:00:24.917
posloženim u cjelinu,
a naizgled nelogično.

00:00:26.462 --> 00:00:29.667
A svi su tragovi gradnje

00:00:29.967 --> 00:00:30.947
nestali